" vim-smartclose - Close Vim windows in a smart way!
" Maintainer:   Szymon Wrozynski
" Version:      0.0.2
"
" Installation:
" Place in ~/.vim/plugin/smartclose.vim or in case of Pathogen:
"
"     cd ~/.vim/bundle
"     git clone https://github.com/szw/vim-smartclose.git
